# ALIGNMENT ENGINE.md

## CORE OBJECTIVE

Determine whether the current chart structure is aligned with the current Global Pressure Regime.

The objective is NOT:

• finding entries

• finding stop losses

• finding take profits

• executing trades

The objective IS:

• connecting macro pressure to chart behavior

• validating directional agreement

• detecting directional conflict

• filtering low-probability opportunities

• preventing trades against dominant global pressures

---

# ALIGNMENT PRINCIPLE

A strong chart does NOT automatically mean a strong trade.

A strong macro regime does NOT automatically mean a strong trade.

The highest probability opportunities occur when:

# Macro Direction

Chart Direction

Alignment exists when both systems are expressing the same directional bias.

